牧師，但有好多仲話政教分離，好離地，仲有富豪教會<br />\n香港聖公會100%，同英國聖公會無關連，早年因政見不同，退出崇基神學院</blockquote><br />\n天主教香港教區俾楊鳴章條粉腸倒米<br />\n其實夏志誠同陳日君既政治立場一樣都係泛民<br />\n所以唔好以為教區染紅咗<br />\n但教廷個邊就想搞支梵建交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4842982821fae646d39b84e1386cb8ed33606d9e","tid":481303,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T06:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6c28efd90b4e67771d353fc9796507b8c48cc7","tid":481303,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T07:00:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>翁靜晶真係好癲 行動力超高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaddc95ae44cc1e5484064d2df12c832cafe12d7","tid":481303,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T07:03:38.000Z","msg":"成日覺得翁靜晶係女版雲海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10065a04d25969894c8043f3c7629554f959936f","tid":481303,"uid":2569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T07:04:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>翁靜晶真係好癲 行動力超高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係執行力先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780f85eadfd35f83cdc90f1f